					<p>
					<?php
					_e(
						'All of the best performing sharing interfaces have one thing in common: a contact picker. It\'s the proven way to grow your website visitors virally because it\'s the best interface for your users to input a long list of email addresses into your invitation form. Without a contact picker, your users will have to type emails into your invitation form manually or copy and paste them from another window.
						<br/>
						<br/>
						Better Sharing\'s integration with CloudSponge\'s Contact Picker plugs all of the popular webmail address book providers into your website instantly. Your users will be able to select and input all of their friends\' email addresses directly from Google Contacts, Yahoo Mail, Outlook.com, Microsoft 365, AOL, iCloud, and dozens more around the world.
						<br/>
						<br/>
						Here\'s how:
						<ol>
							<li><a href="https://app.cloudsponge.com/v3/app/signup" target="_blank">Create a CloudSponge account</a></li>
							<li>Create a new project to get your CloudSponge Key</li>
							<li>Paste your CloudSponge Key below. You can find your key in a project <a href="https://app.cloudsponge.com/v3/app/projects" target="_blank">in your CloudSponge Dashboard</a>.</li>
							<li>Follow the setup instructions provided by CloudSponge</li>
							<li><a href="https://www.cloudsponge.com/contact/" target="_blank">Contact the CloudSponge team</a> if you have any questions</li>
						</ol>'
					);
					?>
					<br/></p> 
